data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Pace, FL—a move-in ready gem that offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. This charming residence features 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, providing ample space for your family's needs. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a thoughtfully designed split open floor plan, allowing for both privacy and seamless interaction. The centerpiece of the home is the spacious and inviting open kitchen, complete with stainless steel appliances that cater to the culinary enthusiast in you. The kitchen flows seamlessly into the den and dining areas, making it an ideal space for entertaining and creating cherished memories with loved ones. Imagine enjoying the fresh air and the tranquility of the outdoors right from the comfort of your home. Double glass doors in the den lead to a delightful outdoor patio area, perfect for relaxation and al fresco dining. Whether it's sipping your morning coffee or hosting a barbecue, this outdoor space is sure to become a favorite retreat. The soothing color palette throughout the home creates a calm and inviting atmosphere, making it easy to unwind and recharge. The travertine flooring in the kitchen, baths, and laundry area adds an elegant touch to the space, combining style with easy maintenance. Location is everything, and this home doesn't disappoint. Centrally located, It's just a quick 30-minute drive away from the vibrant downtown area of Pensacola, where you can enjoy shopping, dining, and entertainment. A 30-minute drive if you're a beach enthusiast, Pensacola Beach is also within easy reach, allowing you to soak up the sun and enjoy the pristine Gulf Coast. Whether you're looking for a comfortable family home or a place to unwind and enjoy the Florida lifestyle, this move-in ready property in Pace, FL, has it all.
